Make Sure They Accept Your Invitation 
  
  
  
    

  

Cristina, 

        


We contacted the contributor using the email you entered in your 2026–27 Free Application for Federal Student Aid  (FAFSA ® )  form. 



Their invitation email includes a link that will take them to the FAFSA form. You can also send them the following invitation link or code if they can't find the invitation email. 

Invitation Link: 

 https://studentaid.gov/fafsa-apply/2026-27/accept-invitation/7TTDR66 https://studentaid.gov/fafsa-apply/2026-27/accept-invitation/7TTDR66

Invitation Code: 

7TTDR66  
  
  
    

  
Manage Contributors 

Log in to see contributor invitations and codes. Select your FAFSA form on your "My Activity" page to view contributors. You can also remove or replace contributors if needed. 
  

